{"tid":210200,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"宋冬野 2017 新歌 — 《空港曲》","createTime":"2017-04-20T18:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T13:40:08.000Z","uid":4260,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55f80e0a5c2a97cc24bed69f110b339fd8cdb171","tid":210200,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:08:04.000Z","msg":"宋冬野【空港曲】官方歌詞版 MV <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MZ2H9XGEFmY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMZ2H9XGEFmY&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b484b6d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MZ2H9XGEFmY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「經過整個團隊近半年共同的努力，我們完成了幾首新曲，過程裡我搞懂了很多一直搞不懂的問題，學會了很多一直難以企及的東西，終於也敢自稱是個真正的音樂人了。今天的《空港曲》是新曲其中之一，褒貶請隨意。」<br />\n<br />\n宋冬野 微博"},{"pid":"e7ebbc3612b9063ccbf983c142a6a590e5c48582","tid":210200,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:08:24.000Z","msg":"詞/曲：宋冬野<br />\n<br />\n髒水洗身 濁杯赴宴<br />\n欲辯忘言 忘言欲辯<br />\n戲子與員警又念起詩篇<br />\n盜賊 王臣 謊言<br />\n<br />\n如來的飯碗 荒誕世間<br />\n你我登船 送命或尋歡<br />\n草廬高堂 金光大道<br />\n閑雲 牛馬 殺人刀<br />\n<br />\n可春色不過宛若江南<br />\n可月色不過對影三人<br />\n可藝術之王垂死於度量<br />\n可信仰不過是忘記真相<br />\n<br />\n但願病重的醫生心有餘悸<br />\n但願一切親吻 不悲不喜<br />\n但願不在此時此地<br />\n但願誰都不在意<br />\n<br />\n編曲：宋冬野<br />\n製作人：宋冬野<br />\n尺八：宋冬野<br />\n柔音號：史立<br />\n吉他：鄭仕偉<br />\n貝斯：鄭仕偉<br />\n鼓：張超<br />\n和聲/合唱：宋冬野、陳泯西、劉郡格、吳金迪、祖力卡爾、周冠辰、鄭仕偉<br />\n錄音/混音：鄭仕偉（Music Flow Studio）"},{"pid":"8ce4f9a9f7b8dc2c28b493750404e278b7246756","tid":210200,"uid":28019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:09:42.000Z","msg":"同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffab19b1cc452c60593fddce835520bb6f8e1f6","tid":210200,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:12:02.000Z